latestPosts.caption:
🎉 A dream come true moment for us! 🧡

Behind every planner shipped, every carton sealed, and every sticker packed is hours of dedication, countless sleepless nights, and boundless gratitude. 🙏✨

This week, we packed and shipped thousands of orders—each one carrying a piece of our heart and a promise to make your 2025 more vibrant, organized, and joyful. 🌸📆

Seeing your love for our handmade planners and calendars from the Gulmohar Collection has left us overwhelmed and inspired to keep creating. From the colors we paint to the affirmations we write, it’s all for YOU. 💕

Here’s to crafting dreams and sending them to every corner of the country—and maybe beyond. 🌍 Thank you for making this launch a roaring success. YOU made this happen. 🌟

💌 With love and gratitude,
Rashi & the Roohanirang Design Studio Team

🌿 Shop handmade. Support small. 🌿

#HandmadeWithLove #IndianArtisans #PlannerAddict #2025Planner #SmallBusinessLove #RecycledPaper #EcoFriendlyLiving #IndianDesign #PlannerCommunity #SupportSmallBusiness #HandcraftedDesigns #MentalWellnessMatters #ArtForTheSoul #VibrantPlanners #GulmoharCollection #roohanirang

A Journey of Resilience and Creativity 🌸

When we decided to take Roohanirang Design Studio from the cozy streets of Surat to the bustling city of Mumbai, we knew it would be a challenge—but we had no idea just how much.

From getting scammed (more details in next post) in the chaos of this big city to 20-hour workdays filled with sweat, tears, and endless cups of chai, the road has been anything but easy. Yet, through it all, our vision remained unwavering: to craft a collection that feels as vibrant and soulful as the spirit of Roohanirang.

This collection is so close to our hearts. Every design, every detail, and every handmade product is a testament to resilience, love, and the sheer determination to make art that inspires.

All struggles may come , but it also just makes us stronger. And now, we’re so proud to share this labor of love with all of you. 💛✨

Thank you for supporting not just our work, but our journey. Here’s to dreaming big and never giving up.

#NewCollection #HandmadeWithLove #RoohanirangDesignStudio #MadeInMumbai #ResilientArt

latestPosts.caption:
Hi, I’m Rashi, the heart behind Roohanirang Design Studio. 🌸

Today, I’m writing to share something very close to my heart—our Gulmohar collection. It feels surreal to finally see it come to life after months of dreaming, planning, and creating. This collection holds so much love and effort, and I hope it brings as much joy to you as it did to me while making it.

Truth be told, being an entrepreneur is a journey of its own. Some days are filled with excitement, while others are quiet and challenging. There have been countless moments when I wondered if I was on the right path. It’s not always easy to keep going when the world feels a little lonely, but then there’s this—this joy of bringing an idea to life, of holding something tangible that once existed only in my mind.

The Gulmohar collection is my way of sharing that joy with you. Each piece, whether it’s the desk calendar with hand-drawn affirmations or the coloring scrapbook made with flower-petal craft paper, is a little reminder of hope, creativity, and the beauty of slowing down. Every card, page, and sticker is infused with the colors of India, the love of our artisans, and the belief that small, meaningful things can brighten even the hardest days.

More than anything, this collection is a testament to resilience—the resilience of the artisans who bring these designs to life, and my own as I navigate this unpredictable yet deeply rewarding journey.

Thank you for being here, for reading this, for even considering supporting what we do. You may not realize it, but every kind word, every purchase, and even just your encouragement means the world to me and to the artisans who work alongside me.

If you have a moment, I’d love for you to take a look at what we’ve created. Even if it’s just to feel the warmth and love that went into every piece.

With all my heart,
Rashi 🌸

P.S. Thank you for being part of this story—it wouldn’t be the same without you.

#GulmoharCollection #MadeWithLove #RoohanirangStories #ArtisanCrafted #FromMyHeartToYours #SmallBusinessJourney #SustainableArt
